info.author: Karsten Koenig
info.description: A simple renamer written in Python with PyQt4. cuteRenamer will rename the files of a directory sequentially, that is they will be numbered serially. You need PyQt4 to run cuteRenamer.
info.name: cuteRenamer
info.summary: A simple renamer written in Python with some nice options.
